// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6929 — Mass File Rename (threeam)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c9c50902-418e-546d-baa9-3f9273724358

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
